All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, LocationScheduleElement, NewLocationScheduleElement, NewScheduleElement, ScheduleElement, TimeSpan
public abstract class TaggedLocationScheduleElement
extends LocationScheduleElementImpl

A LocationScheduleElement which is additionally tagged with an additional piece of information, normally the "owner" of the schedule information. It is up to (non-abstract) subclasses to decide how to implement getOwner().
